Interface PrfFixed

  • All Superinterfaces:
    PseudorandomFunction
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AES, PrpFixed, TripleDES
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BcAES, BcPRP, BcTripleDES, CryptoPpAES, MiraclAES, OpenSSLAES, OpenSSLPRP, OpenSSLTripleDES, PrpFromPrfFixed

    public interface PrfFixed
extends PseudorandomFunction
    General interface for pseudorandom function with fixed input and output lengths. A pseudorandom function with fixed lengths predefined input and output lengths, and there is no need to specify it for each function call.

    Cryptography and Computer Security Research Group Department of Computer Science Bar-Ilan University (Meital Levy)
